# Lab07 - React Shopping App
## Goal
* TODO-1: Increase / Decrease item amount
* TODO-2, 3: Add to shopping cart and show items
* TODO-4: Calculate and display total price
* TODO-5: Clear the shopping cart
* TODO-6: Remove specific item in shopping cart
* TODO-7: Pay money
* TODO-8, 9: Input value and charge money 


## Grading Policy
**Deadline: 2024/04/16 17:20 (No late demo or submission!)**
* Increase / Decrease item amount - 20%
* Add to shopping cart and show items - 20%
* Calculate and display total price - 10%
* Clear the shopping cart - 10%
* Remove specific item in shopping cart - 10%
* Pay money correctly - 20%
* Input and charge money correctly - 10%
